text: "Miss America" is a song recorded by Swedish singer Måns Zelmerlöw. It was released on 5 May 2008 as a digital download in Sweden. It was released as the fourth single from his studio album Stand by For... (2007). The song was written by Fredrik Kempe. It peaked to number 47 on the Swedish Singles Chart.
